# Project Roadmap

## Phase 1: Foundation (Q1 - Q2 2024)
- Completion of core platform architecture and infrastructure.
- Development of automation modules for key Web3 processes.
- Initial integrations with major blockchain protocols.
- Internal testing and security audits.

## Phase 2: Beta Launch (Q3 2024)
- Open beta release to selected community members and partners.
- Collection of feedback and iterative improvements.
- Expansion of integration options.
- User experience enhancements based on real-world use.

## Phase 3: Public Launch (Q4 2024)
- General availability for all Web3 developers and teams.
- Comprehensive documentation and training resources.
- Marketing campaigns to build awareness.

## Phase 4: Expansion and Evolution (2025 and beyond)
- Introduction of advanced features such as AI-driven analytics and predictive project insights.
- Support for emerging blockchain platforms and standards.
- Continuous security improvements and compliance.
- Growth of ecosystem partnerships and developer community.

## Key Milestones
- Secure first 100 active projects using LLM Studio.
- Achieve platform scalability to support thousands of concurrent users.
- Establish strategic collaborations with leading blockchain entities.

